<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4315443>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 35. Astacilla frigida (Hansen, 1916). A–C, male syntype (ZMUC CRU 9403), 8.5 mm. A, habitus, dorsal view; B, habitus, lateral view; C, pereopod 1, detail distally; D–J, male (ZMH–K–39770). D, pereopod 4, distal part; E, pereopod 5, distal part; F, pereopod 6, distal part; G, uropod, distal end; H, penial plate; I, pleopod 1 (apical setae omitted on exopod); J, pleopod 2. Scales: a, b = 1 mm (A, B); c–j = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4315443/files/figure.png" .

